items.short_desc: From Buttler's 124 to Dhawan's 69*, Akhil and Arun discuss all the excellent individual performances from Sunday. They also credit Rajasthan and Delhi for their win. Watch the video to find more insights of the game.
items.asset_title: Timeout with SportsAdda | IPL 2021 | Match 28 & 29 Review

items.short_desc: Ridhima Pathak, Akhil Ranade and Arun are here with a complete dose of entertainment on episode 3 of Doubtful Review System.
items.asset_title: \"Cricket is a religion, cricket is a healer\" | DRS: Season 2 - Episode 3 | IPL 2021

items.short_desc: Manish Batavia starts by thanking Brett Lee for his lovely gesture last week. The two of them then discuss how teams did in the past week and preview Gameweek 4 of the Indian T20 League. The Aussie pacer gives his predictions and speaks about some talented individual performances so far.
items.asset_title: Brett Lee: Mumbai vs Chennai is going to be a cracker | T20 Crazy on SportsAdda | IPL 2021

items.short_desc: Akhil and Arun have a long discussion on how the two teams from the top-half of the table had a stroll on the park. They emphasize on what went right for Mumbai and what went wrong for Morgan. The duo then shift their focus on tonight's clash where KL Rahul's men take on Virat Kohli's army and give their match predictions.
items.asset_title: Timeout with SportsAdda | IPL 2021 | Match 26 | Punjab's need to bounce back

items.short_desc: Watch Akhil and Arun discuss last night's one-sided clash between Chennai and Hyderabad before they welcome Apurv to share some wonderful cricketing stories, almost taking us back to the '90s. They then discuss today's double-header and pick their favourites to win the games.
items.asset_title: Timeout with SportsAdda | IPL 2021 | Match 24 & 25 | Will Rajasthan topple the defending champions?
